title: "ApiStatusAlert"
description: "Pure Astro. Renders a deprecated, unstable, or beta status banner for an endpoint."
type: static
---

# ApiStatusAlert

An alert banner for API endpoint status: deprecated, unstable, or beta. Supports slot content for the message body.

## Properties

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `type` | `string` | — | One of: deprecated, unstable, beta. Controls the label, color, and default message |
| `newerVersionUrl` | `string` | — | Link to newer version (shown for deprecated type) |
| `message` | `string` | Type-specific default | Custom message override |

## Examples

### Deprecated

{% tabs %}
{% tab label="Result" %}
{% apiStatusAlert type="deprecated" %}
This endpoint is deprecated.
{% /apiStatusAlert %}
{% /tab %}
{% tab label="Markdoc" %}
```markdoc
{% apiStatusAlert type="deprecated" %}
This endpoint is deprecated.
{% /apiStatusAlert %}
```
{% /tab %}
{% /tabs %}

### Deprecated with newer version link

{% tabs %}
{% tab label="Result" %}
{% apiStatusAlert type="deprecated" newerVersionUrl="/api/latest/dashboards/" %}
This endpoint is deprecated.
{% /apiStatusAlert %}
{% /tab %}
{% tab label="Markdoc" %}
```markdoc
{% apiStatusAlert type="deprecated" newerVersionUrl="/api/latest/dashboards/" %}
This endpoint is deprecated.
{% /apiStatusAlert %}
```
{% /tab %}
{% /tabs %}

### Unstable

{% tabs %}
{% tab label="Result" %}
{% apiStatusAlert type="unstable" %}
